# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The CORE pipeline (make up: download → load → profile → dbt run → dbt test
# → dashboard) needs NONE of these. They are read ONLY by the AI edge layers
# (make scaffold / make orchestrate / make ask).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Anthropic key for the AI layers. Alternatively drop a one-line `anthropic.txt`
# at the repo root. If neither is set, the AI targets print a clear message and
# the deterministic core still runs.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Per-layer model routing (sensible defaults baked in; override to taste).
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL_L1=claude-sonnet-4-6
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL_L2=claude-sonnet-4-6
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL_L7=claude-haiku-4-5

# Which dataset the AI layers target by default (a folder under datasets/).
# DATASET=anage
